room_title: Escape room "Aftermath" by Method of Escape in Fresno
room_description:
You and your team were selected through a lottery system to have a coveted spot in a Tech-Tomb, an underground bunker designed for the possibility of nuclear war. It was supposed to keep you safe in a cryo-freeze for the next 200 years until you wake up to re-inhabit the earth.
Due to a mechanical failure, you have awoken early to find that you have about 60 minutes of oxygen left. Can you disable the security system and open the door before it's too late? The air is getting thin...
